{
  "stem": "12684.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Things what-- topics you would otherwise not talk about, like what do you think you want to do on your birthday, or the second birthday after the war has ended.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, so you make plans, which you never realize, but you talk about them, and it makes you want to live for nothing else.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I always said, I want to have my birthday under palms.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I want to have the holidays under palms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It took me many years.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had my birthday under palms and the holidays under palms in Barbados, of course.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a ration of bread, which-- of bread, which we got.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know how much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That much, perhaps.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you had that for three days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And sometimes you were so hungry, you wanted to eat it in one day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So then people would go and steal somebody else's bread, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or you do a favor for somebody for a little piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in the afternoon, as well as in the evening, there were rations.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They came, and you came with your little whatever it was, a plate, or whatever you could get your food in-- soup, or vegetables, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't think I ever ate so much horse meat in my life as there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The only time in my life I know I are horse meat, and I never want to eat it again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because people talked about it, but meat is meat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I do remember one of the religious Jewish people said, even to the very kosher ones, you have to eat the meat.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Rules do not apply anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And they were not plentiful.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you wouldn't starve from them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Really, you wouldn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It just keeps you alive, vaguely.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
